OL,3,CWhen do the clocks change and why does
OL,4,Cit happen?
OL,6,FThe clocks go forward on Sunday,
OL,7,Fmarking the beginning of British
OL,8,FSummer Time (BST).
OL,10,FThis marks the end of Greenwich Mean
OL,11,FTime (GMT) and will mean longer,
OL,12,Flighter evenings from next week.
OL,14,FBut when exactly will the clocks
OL,15,Fchange, and why does it happen?
OL,17,FWhen will the clocks change?
OL,19,FThe clocks go forward at 1am on the
OL,20,Flast Sunday in March. This year that
OL,21,Fwill be on March 30.
