OL,6,FWhat is the difference between British
OL,7,FSummer Time (BST) and Greenwich Mean
OL,8,FTime (GMT)?
OL,10,FGMT was the default legal time used in
OL,11,FBritain before DST was introduced.
OL,12,FThis means when the clocks go back,
OL,13,Fthe country returns to the default
OL,14,Ftime zone introduced in Britain in
OL,15,F1880.
OL,17,FContrary to popular belief, the time
OL,18,Fjump was not introduced to benefit
OL,19,Ffarmers. In fact, farmers were never
OL,20,Fconsulted.
