OL,6,FHe published a pamphlet called The
OL,7,FWaste Of Daylight, which outlined his
OL,8,Ffrustration with not getting the most
OL,9,Fout of summer days.
OL,11,FHe initially proposed that clocks jump
OL,12,Fforward by 80 minutes in four steps in
OL,13,FApril and reversed the same way in
OL,14,FSeptember.
OL,16,FHe died before any law was implemented
OL,17,Fin the UK, but his great-great-
OL,18,Fgrandson, Coldplay singer Chris
OL,19,FMartin, has seen it in action.
