OL,6,FThe first country to adopt DST was
OL,7,FGermany in 1916, during the First
OL,8,FWorld War. The UK followed suit a few
OL,9,Fweeks later.
OL,11,FWhat are the benefits of the clocks
OL,12,Fgoing forward?
OL,14,FDr Jeffrey Kelu, circadian rhythms
OL,15,Fexpert at King's College London, says
OL,16,Fthere can be a number of arguments for
OL,17,FDST.
