OL,6,F"I think there are some suggestions
OL,7,Fthat there is less crime because more
OL,8,Fpeople are out there in the evening
OL,9,Fand it is harder to commit crimes," he
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,F"Also there are fewer traffic
OL,13,Faccidents because there is more light
OL,14,Fand people can see the traffic
